"""
reit2csv - Canadian & US REIT Price Scrape + Cache

Version: 1.2

This script fetches real-time stock prices for Canadian and US REITs using Yahoo Finance. It ensures data integrity by maintaining timestamps for unchanged values and only runs during market hours (9:30 AM - 4:00 PM EST).

It saves the collected data to a CSV file which can be used to source your spreadsheet or application.

